      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that still looks and feels great? I'm parting with my car, and it has been such a joy to drive! It\u2019s in solid shape, runs super smoothly, and has been really well-loved. Whether you're commuting to work or heading out on a fun weekend getaway, this beauty is ready to hit the road with you. Grab it while it's still available\u2014you're going to love it!",
      "price": 34500.0,
