    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a well-maintained example of high-revving German engineering, powered by the S54 3.2L inline-six engine featuring individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. The drivetrain is paired with a precise 6-speed manual transmission and a factory-spec limited-slip differential, ensuring linear power delivery and exceptional rear-end grip. The chassis remains rigid with an inspected rear subframe and refreshed suspension bushings for sharp turn-in response. Recent preventative maintenance includes a cooling system overhaul and valve clearance adjustment, ensuring the engine pulls cleanly to its 8,000 RPM redline. A mechanically sorted driver's car ready for the canyons.",
      "price": 34500.0,
