    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained 2019 Audi A6 that perfectly balances executive luxury with everyday utility. This vehicle has been a reliable companion, consistently serviced at authorized dealerships with a full digital service history available for your review. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous metallic shine; while it looks stunning at a glance, a close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear passenger-side alloy wheel\u2014honest wear that reflects its life as a cherished commuter. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary. The premium Valcona leather upholstery is supple and free of any tears or unsightly bolster wear, and the dual-screen MMI touch response system operates flawlessly. All electronic components, including the 16-speaker Bang & Olufsen sound system and the panoramic sunroof, are in perfect working order. Mechanically, the car is robust; the 3.0L V6 engine pulls cleanly, the transmission shifts are imperceptible, and the brakes were recently serviced with new pads and rotors. This is a smoke-free, pet-free vehicle that has been kept in a climate-controlled garage. It offers a sophisticated driving experience for those who appreciate quality and mechanical integrity.",
